<br>
Well if someone started there, they would miss all the Claremont/Byrne stuff and all the Cockrum/Claremont stuff. That is some amazing stuff. The Phoenix Saga, The Brood, Corsair and the Starjammers, Days of Future Past, The Death of Phoenix, and on and on! Those are some amazing story arcs. <br>
<br>
If one were to be really intrested in picking those up, I'd recommend the Essential X-Men books. They're resonably priced and contain a lot of issues. The only drawback is they are black and white, but that's a small price to pay to get that many great stories. <br>
<br>
